<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp;...<br />&nbsp;ld a,&#40;hl&#41;<br />&nbsp;inc hl<br />&nbsp;ld h,&#40;hl&#41;<br />&nbsp;ld l,a<br />&nbsp;jp &#40;hl&#41;</div>

		

