<br />
<br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Normally, in porting Donkey Kong, the quickest way would have been to use the CPU in the arcade version. But Ricoh wanted us to use the 6502, which they had the license for. When I said I wanted to use the 6502 at Nintendo, the staff told me that I make such decisions because I didnâ€™t make video games.</div>

		

